data.description: **2.99% ASSUMABLE INTEREST RATE** Step inside this charming, move-in-ready home in the desirable Sawmill Creek community, located just off US-1. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a 2.99% assumable mortgage, making it a fantastic opportunity for the savvy buyer! As you enter, you'll be captivated by the open floor plan that creates a sense of spaciousness and flow throughout the living spaces. Built in 2021, this home is practically brand new! The kitchen features granite countertops and tile flooring that extends seamlessly through the living spaces. This home provides the perfect canvas to add your personal touch and make it your own. Situated on a beautiful fully-fenced preserve lot, you'll enjoy tranquility and privacy, with nature as your backdrop. Additionally, the Sawmill Creek community offers a refreshing pool for residents to cool off and relax. Don't miss this opportunity to own a newer home with an assumable mortgage in a fantastic location. Don’t miss out on this 2.99% interest rate-it’s a deal you won’t want to pass up!
